file.name: config-no-query.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  title: 'Example site'
  version: 0.1.0
x-walder-resources:
  root: .
  views: views
paths:
  /:
    get:
      summary: Show text
      responses:
        200:
          description: a text
          x-walder-input-text/html: text.pug
x-walder-errors:
  404:
    description: page not found error
    x-walder-input-text/html: error404.html
  500:
    description: internal server error
    x-walder-input-text/html: error500.html
